{
  "stem": "15393.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Primarily, they liked his work, because his work was not simply just, just a little table or something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was done.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was finished.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He thought about what it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was done intelligently, put it this way, maybe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that made the difference between just an ordinary carpenter and him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were always sort of come and looking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How is it-- how is he doing this [INAUDIBLE] smoothly, so nicely?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they liked him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they forever sent some things for the children, the home, via him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russian officers were, you know, very nice to him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he didn't trust them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At one point, not very long after [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the occupation, they put out notices all over town that anybody who wishes to go back to their homes on the other side of the river San, which is to the German-occupied part of Poland, is welcome to do so.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If they have families there, if they left families there, if they're here on their own, they are welcome to do so.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Would they please come and register on such-and-such a day, and they can go back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, there were a lot of, particularly, men who were on their own, because they were taken to the army.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When everything was dismantled and, you know, disarray, they, like my father, came, escaped on their own.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there they were.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The whole family would have stayed behind, not like we.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were unique in, in the sense that we were a unit, a family unit on this side.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They usually-- the man went to the army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The family stayed behind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And a lot of them were coming to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were friends from Cracow, and so they were coming.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
